data.description: Welcome to Hayne's Station! 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a split bedroom floor plan and a bonus room that connects the foyer to the front bedroom. The heart of this ranch home is the open-concept living space, seamlessly connecting the living room, dining area, and kitchen. Natural light floods the rooms, enhancing the already generous sense of space. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, wine fridge and large pantry. Interior of the home has been recently painted and all new carpet throughout! Owner's suite is separate from the other bedrooms and includes a spacious closet and ensuite with double sink vanity, storage and garden tub. Two additional bedrooms and a full bath are located on the other side of the living room from the owner's suite. Step outside to the expansive, fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining or enjoying time outdoors. Conveniently located off Gordon Highway, you'll find yourself in close proximity to Fort Eisenhower, restaurants, highway, shopping and more. VA loan 2.25 assumable rate! Contact us or your agent for more information.
